description: This Chainlink VRF common Sakura purrs with a rating of 53, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 106, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, Leverage for East, Stringalong for South, and Nine Lives for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10532-26790-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [106 Votes, Common]
